\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Here is a comprehensive overview of the competitive landscape in Belgium for your external consultancy. It includes links to the major players, an explanation of what they do, and\'97most importantly\'97how you beat them.\
You can use this directly as a briefing document for your consultants.\
